snippet.title: Truck & Logistics Simulator (2017 Video)
snippet.description:
This video was recorded in 2017 and it doesn't represent the current state of the game. For up to date videos please check the playlist linked below.
Truck & Logistics Simulator was previously known as "Transport Company Simulator" and "Delivery Simulator" and its name has changed.

"Truck & Logistics Simulator" playlist (for up to date videos): https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLWA_kZhzrNQsjC-9owUGA3Ciwosp9HyiA

[Turkish] Bu video 2017 yılında kaydedilmiştir ve oyunun günümüzdeki halini yansıtmamaktadır. Oyunun güncel halini görmek istiyorsanız aşağıdaki oynatma listesi linkiyle güncel videolara ulaşabilirsiniz.
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLWA_kZhzrNQs-K8J_xzBiS1fj_8gjL-hn

Oyunda iki kez isim değişikliğine gidildi. Önceki isimleri "Delivery Simulator" ve "Transport Company Simulator"

Website: www.simulagames.com
